		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I fixed this already.<br /><br /><a href="http://www.romhacking.net/forum/index.php/topic,16035.0.html" class="postlink">http://www.romhacking.net/forum/index.php/topic,16035.0.html</a><br /><br />The problem was at the beginning of the stage the game was doing writes that were setting it to run as a 512k rom, colorizer needs the game to be running as 1mbyte.  The writes weren't necessary for the game to function so I just removed them.

		

